The paper proposes a novel training procedure for GANs to improve stability and performance in unsupervised image generation. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and graphics (cs.GR).
